<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Happy Birthday</title>

<style>
body{
    font-family: Arial;
    background:#f4f4f4;
    padding:20px;
}

.container{
    max-width:600px;
    margin:auto;
    background:white;
    padding:30px;
    border-radius:8px;
    text-align:center;
}

.header{
    background:#3b82f6;
    color:white;
    padding:15px;
    border-radius:5px;
    font-size:22px;
}

.footer{
    margin-top:20px;
    color:#666;
    font-size:14px;
}
</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<div class="header">
🎂 Happy Birthday
</div>

<h2>Hello <%= name %></h2>

<p>Wishing you a very Happy Birthday!</p>

<p>May your year be filled with health, happiness and strength.</p>

<h3>Enjoy your workout today 💪</h3>

<div class="footer">
Best Wishes,<br>
Chava Gym
</div>

</div>

</body>

</html>